{"tid":733916,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"于日辰/李文晉 先生啟： 糟糠之妻不下堂。","createTime":"2018-07-08T07:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T13:16:50.000Z","uid":11055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d14959399cfc71f0f30267bc71544fbcc256ff74","tid":733916,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"《後漢書》：「臣聞貧賤之知不可忘，糟糠之妻不下堂。」<br />\n<br />\n《聊齋志異&middot;八大王》：「糟糠之妻不下堂，寧死不敢承命，王如聽臣自贖，傾家可也。」<br />\n<br />\n實如史文、小說所記，糟糠以承貧賤，<br />\n毋嫌閣下之一無所有；<br />\n毋患閣下之五肢疲幼。<br />\n獨何如？<br />\n<br />\n唉，當你唔撚識咁多喇，<br />\n爛賭夫鬥爛賭妻有冇睇過？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日扮情聖，扮文豪，<br />\n「在天願作比翼鳥，在地願為連理枝。」<br />\n都唔學習下，靠寫甜故上位，<br />\n上左位之後就學人先抬身價？<br />\n你以為自己真係現代唐伯虎，當代王世貞啊？<br />\n你寫咸書架咋死咸蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n冚家富貴<br />\n<br />\n楊槙<br />\n貳零壹捌年<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">柒</span></span>月捌日"},{"pid":"4c8de2f18c5bf14f2509c1426979335b7c9b2cfd","tid":733916,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"建議巴打拋書包之前，不妨搞清楚依個情況用啟係咪合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}